 Fast Fourier Transform (FFT) type\nmethods. The resulting numerical methods allow efficient implementation on\nparallel computers. Numerical results confirm the high efficiency of the\nproposed iterative approach.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 6 Dec 2012 17:54:45 GMT"}],"update_date":"2012-12-07"}
